<p local-id=3D"947d32ff-755c-4383-b55f-f97199c800de">To change to UK format=
, you need to amend your default browser language and your user settings in=
 Azure board</p>
<p local-id=3D"9602da30-0f60-451f-9a25-50c96dd36da4">Browser: <a class=3D"e=
