vops-board-wont-let-me-change-the-time-date-format" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>dat=
etime - Azure DevOps board won't let me change the time/date format - Stack=
 Overflow</u></a></p>
<p local-id=3D"207a5554-ec2b-4af8-8277-108903c596c8">Azure Board: <a class=
=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/60750587/how=
-to-change-the-date-format-on-a-work-item-in-azure-devops-work-item" rel=3D=
"nofollow"><u>How to change the date format on a Work Item in Azure DevOps =
Work item - Stack Overflow</u></a></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-fi=
le-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=
