<li local-id=3D"eda0e50d-169b-410d-baec-3f9ada74d6e4">
<p local-id=3D"8a1bc633-7996-4d79-a682-d23a7f5b3f16"><strong>Explanation:</=
strong> The board uses <strong>swimlanes as Team Backlogs</strong>. Items s=
houldn=E2=80=99t sit in the <strong>board backlog</strong> for long =E2=80=
=94 they should move to the appropriate team backlog/swimlane.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3169d50-8293-4990-812f-0c5120ec1b63">
<p local-id=3D"0addc2d0-c328-40a1-ba3e-bef48f7e32cd"><strong>How to fix:</s=
trong> Triage the item =E2=86=92 decide which team should own it =E2=86=92 =
set the correct <strong>Area Path</strong> and move it into the appropriate=
 team backlog.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b23ef0be-11fa-401d-9d2d-74d8acce598c">
<p local-id=3D"934987b0-0b96-4f6f-9461-846b2648a9ec"><strong>Fixed CoS But =
No LRM Date</strong></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper ima=
ge-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-e=
mbedded-image image-left" alt=3D"image-20260227-131240.png" width=3D"468" l=
oading=3D"lazy" src=3D"1f09b880626d27f683606b15aed64f163c63c2e9a437c96556ab=
a6550869a043" data-image-src=3D"https://emishealthgroup.atlassian.net/wiki/=
download/attachments/8489566320/image-20260227-131240.png?version=3D1&amp;m=
odificationDate=3D1772197963863&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-hei=
ght=3D"214" data-width=3D"662" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-lin=
ked-resource-id=3D"8650031484" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-link=
ed-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image=
-20260227-131240.png" data-base-url=3D"https://emishealthgroup.atlassian.ne=
